data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.100 set value "The wheat's looking good this season."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.101 set value "Mind the scarecrow—he's doing his best."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.102 set value "Sun's high, crops are dry, time to water."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.103 set value "Saw a Patron out by the old ruins yesterday. Gold symbol, mythical tier."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.104 set value "If you see a pillager, don't wave."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.105 set value "Nothing like the smell of fresh hay."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.106 set value "The cows have been jumpy lately. Maybe it's the Dream Surge."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.107 set value "Sunrise here always feels safe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.108 set value "We don't trust foxes near the henhouse."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.109 set value "A strong fence is a peaceful night's sleep."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.110 set value "Trade fair, trade often—that's our way."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.111 set value "There's an old structure crate past the creek. Still hums with magic."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.112 set value "Some folks think the bell keeps monsters away."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.113 set value "Rain's good luck for carrots, bad for boots."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.114 set value "I once saw a creeper get scared of a cat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.115 set value "The wandering trader had miniblocks shaped like tiny oak trees."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.116 set value "Stick to the path and you'll do fine."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.117 set value "We plant potatoes because they listen."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.118 set value "A traveler showed me their Codex once. Pages just kept turning."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.119 set value "The wind talks if you stand still long enough."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.120 set value "Our iron golem's got a name, you know."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.121 set value "These boots? Handmade from tanned leather."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.122 set value "That Expeditionist who passed through? Knew every ruin by heart."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.123 set value "We rotate crops—helps the soil and the soul."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.124 set value "If it squeals in the dark, it ain't a pig."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.125 set value "You ever try milking a mooshroom?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.126 set value "The Heartstone artifact—they say it pulses in time with your own heart."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.127 set value "Nothing beats fresh bread on a foggy morning."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.128 set value "You see clouds, I see weather warnings."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.129 set value "We had a library once—until lightning struck."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.130 set value "Never argue with a farmer holding a hoe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.131 set value "Furia mobs don't have names. Just rage and bad intentions."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.132 set value "It's the little chores that keep you alive."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.133 set value "You can hear wolves at night—sometimes closer."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.134 set value "A good crop can make up for a bad moon."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.135 set value "The grass hums when storms roll in."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.136 set value "My neighbor's kid got a pet hamster from the Companion Catalogue."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.137 set value "The bell rings when danger's close—or dinner's ready."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.138 set value "Bartering is tradition. So is being stubborn."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.139 set value "The fields feed more than stomachs."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.140 set value "Don't whistle after dark—it calls them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.141 set value "Guidestones glow faint blue at dusk. Like little beacons of trust."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.142 set value "There's a slime patch east of the creek."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.143 set value "Stay off the pasture path after midnight."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.144 set value "A Patron with a blue glow stalks the birch grove. Uncommon tier."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.145 set value "Our well is older than the village itself."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.146 set value "Trade me wheat and I'll tell you a secret."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.147 set value "Even scarecrows need a name."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.148 set value "You ever Harmonize two blessings together? Whole new feeling."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.149 set value "I don't trust fences that swing open alone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.150 set value "We bury broken tools under the apple tree."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.151 set value "The plains seem calm—until they're not."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.152 set value "Sometimes the crops whisper old songs."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.153 set value "We once had a priest who talked to sheep."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.154 set value "The Stormcaller artifact crackles even when the sky is clear."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.155 set value "A cat will always find you before a creeper does."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.156 set value "You can tell the weather by the pigs' tails."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.157 set value "Pillagers hate rain—lucky for us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.158 set value "During a Dream Surge, the sky turns violet and the air tastes sweet."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.159 set value "The river runs red in spring—not blood, just berries."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.160 set value "If your hoe glows green, stop digging."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.161 set value "Never ignore the old oak's shadow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.162 set value "An Artificer once fixed our well pump with a single emerald."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.163 set value "A witch once gave us a year of good wheat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.164 set value "Sleep with one eye open if you heard bells twice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.165 set value "Rainwater's fine—if it hasn't shimmered first."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.166 set value "Someone got a mob head drop off a skeleton last week. Rarest thing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.167 set value "We say thanks before cutting the first stalk."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.168 set value "If the wind changes mid-sentence, stop talking."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.169 set value "You brought beets? I suppose I can forgive you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.170 set value "The plains remember who trampled them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.171 set value "My cousin found the Pebble of Dreams in an old crate. Changed him."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.172 set value "You ever feed the horses apples with golden spots?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.173 set value "When the dogs stop barking, get inside."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.174 set value "A Greater Furia zombie came through the fence last full moon."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.175 set value "That patch never grows anything, and we don't ask why."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.176 set value "You ever seen a fox walk backward?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.177 set value "Don't trade on an empty stomach or a full moon."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.178 set value "The Advantage Tree is worth investing in. Pick your branches wisely."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.179 set value "We burn hay in fall to keep the spirits warm."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.180 set value "Sunsets mean more when the wind is still."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.181 set value "Don't pick the red flower near the church."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.182 set value "Dreams are currency now. Strange times we live in."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.183 set value "Some fields grow dreams instead of wheat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.184 set value "The horses never go near the boundary stones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.185 set value "A Beekeeper traded me honey that sparkled. Said her bees were blessed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.186 set value "A rabbit ran through the corn and vanished."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.187 set value "We don't eat meat that doesn't cast a shadow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.188 set value "The windmill hasn't turned in years—and yet it works."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.189 set value "Patrons with the star symbol are the ones you run from."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.190 set value "There's a bell tone only the elders hear."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.191 set value "A boy once vanished chasing a butterfly at dusk."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.192 set value "We don't plow under the twin oaks—ever."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.193 set value "The wandering trader sold plushies last visit. Tiny creeper ones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.194 set value "Trade quick, eat slow—that's how we live."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.195 set value "Horses get spooked when the clouds sit low."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.196 set value "Structure crates refill if you wait long enough. Patience pays."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.197 set value "A shadow moved through the wheat last night."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.198 set value "That house hasn't had a fire lit in years."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.199 set value "The Ruin Watch ticks different near old stone. Like it remembers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.200 set value "Campfires keep stories warm and mobs out."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.201 set value "Morning dew hides secrets in the fields."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.202 set value "An Exquisite Patron walks the ravine at night. Pink glow, named symbol."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.203 set value "Old Thom's scarecrow still guards the wheat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.204 set value "Wolves howl louder when the moon is full."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.205 set value "My dream rate went up after I found that old shrine."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.206 set value "The harvest festival always feels like magic."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.207 set value "A well-aimed arrow saves more than a sword."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.208 set value "The Earthshaker artifact hums low, like thunder trapped in stone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.209 set value "We store our secrets in old oak barrels."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.210 set value "Lightning once split the tallest tree in half."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.211 set value "Weapon mastery comes from doing, not thinking. Swing more."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.212 set value "A good harvest can calm a restless heart."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.213 set value "Don't leave your doors unlocked at dusk."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.214 set value "The river's song changes with the seasons."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.215 set value "A Nymph passed through last spring. Flowers bloomed in her wake."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.216 set value "Mushrooms grow in the shadows of forgotten barns."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.217 set value "There's a fox den near the old millstone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.218 set value "Minor Furia are gray with a little star. Still dangerous enough."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.219 set value "The wind can carry a whisper all the way home."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.220 set value "We always harvest by the light of the moon."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.221 set value "Someone placed a guidestone on the hill. Travel's easier now."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.222 set value "If you find a cracked hoe, it's bad luck."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.223 set value "The barn owl watches over us at night."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.224 set value "Mjolnir. Just the name makes the air feel heavy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.225 set value "The wheat bends but never breaks."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.226 set value "You can tell a good farmer by their boots."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.227 set value "A Hunter tracked a Patron through our fields for three days."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.228 set value "The old well sings when the wind is right."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.229 set value "The bells ring louder when danger is near."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.230 set value "That wandering trader had a name this time. Fancy fellow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.231 set value "The chickens don't cross the path after dark."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.232 set value "Artifacts resonate near the ruins. You can feel it in your teeth."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.233 set value "Foxes steal more than just eggs around here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.234 set value "The scarecrow's eyes glow at midnight."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.235 set value "A friend's kid got a pet phoenix. Warm little thing, always glowing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.236 set value "The harvest moon shines bright on the plains."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.237 set value "Old fences tell stories if you listen closely."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.238 set value "The Blaze Core stays warm even in snow. Unnatural, but useful."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.239 set value "Never ignore the crackling in the dry grass."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.240 set value "A Retired Adventurer settled here. Still flinches at cave noises."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.241 set value "The mill's wheel hasn't stopped turning in years."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.242 set value "We respect the land; it gives us life."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.243 set value "Rare tier Patrons glow aqua. Beautiful and terrifying."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.244 set value "The morning sun warms the soil just right."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.245 set value "Your tomb holds your things if you fall. Small comfort, but still."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.246 set value "A creeper in tall grass is a silent goodbye."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.247 set value "A single seed holds the promise of many."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.248 set value "The Companion Catalogue has a spinosaur in it. A spinosaur!"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.249 set value "Farmers talk to the soil when they think no one's listening."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.250 set value "The Windrunner artifact makes you light on your feet, they say."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.251 set value "A storm can change everything in a heartbeat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.252 set value "The horses know when danger is near before we do."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.253 set value "Ornate Patrons have a purple glow. Regal. Deadly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.254 set value "The sun sets slower here, like it's saying goodbye."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.255 set value "Dream Surges thin the boundaries. Strange loot appears after."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.256 set value "I know every chicken by name here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.257 set value "Every harvest is a story waiting to be told."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.258 set value "The Acacia Ballista is real. Seen one mounted on a ruin wall."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.259 set value "A quiet night can be the most dangerous."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.260 set value "The fields are never truly empty after dark."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.261 set value "A Wise Wanderer told me dreams flow stronger near ancient stone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.262 set value "We keep our secrets locked away with the grain."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.263 set value "The old oak tree remembers everything."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.264 set value "Furia mobs have no loyalty. Just chaos wearing fur and bones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.265 set value "The crops sway like they're dancing in the breeze."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.266 set value "The moonlight makes the wheat shimmer like gold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.267 set value "A Bartender down the road brews something that glows faintly green."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.268 set value "The glow of fireflies marks the safe paths."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.269 set value "Cats watch over the livestock with sharp eyes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.270 set value "The Dragon Boots shimmer like scales. Worth more than this village."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.271 set value "We plant hope with every seed we sow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.272 set value "A single crow can warn of coming storms."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.273 set value "Invest your dreams in the Advantage Tree. It grows with you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.274 set value "The barn doors creak even when no one is near."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.275 set value "The horses' hooves tell stories on the dirt roads."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.276 set value "A Common Patron is gray and quiet. Don't let that fool you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.277 set value "The wind carries laughter and whispers alike."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.278 set value "Strangers bring coin. Trouble brings itself."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.279 set value "A Zookeeper visited with a pet ant colony. Tiny marching soldiers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.280 set value "The river carries more than just water downstream."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.281 set value "The scarecrow keeps its silent vigil through the night."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.282 set value "Structure crates hum louder when they're ready to open again."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.283 set value "The old fence stands strong against time and weather."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.284 set value "Don't follow the road past the old barn."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.285 set value "Furia with a dark red glow and the triple star? Run. Just run."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.286 set value "The river's murmur can soothe the weariest soul."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.287 set value "We say a prayer before planting the first seed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.288 set value "Harmonize your blessings at the right time. Two become something greater."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.289 set value "A rustle in the grass can mean many things."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.290 set value "Lightning struck our stables three times last month."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.291 set value "The Codex tracks every artifact you've touched. Careful what you hold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.292 set value "The fields bloom bright under the midday sun."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.293 set value "Don't trust the quiet spots in the forest."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.294 set value "A Mythical Patron glows gold and has a comet symbol. Like a small god."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.295 set value "The horses neigh softly when dawn breaks."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.296 set value "A storm is brewing beyond the western hills."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.297 set value "A Miner once told me the deepest crates hold the rarest dreams."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.298 set value "Beware the crook in the road by the sycamore."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.299 set value "We keep the harvest safe in old wooden crates."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.300 set value "Could you build us a watchtower on the hill? We need eyes up high."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.301 set value "The ruins east of here have carvings in a language no one reads."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.302 set value "Think you could lay a proper path through the wheat fields?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.303 set value "Bedrock carvings beneath the old temple depict something with wings."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.304 set value "Can you build a scarecrow ring? Seven of them, facing inward."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.305 set value "The old ones built corridors that go nowhere. Or everywhere."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.306 set value "I need a grain silo. A real tall one, with a ladder inside."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.307 set value "Some say the ruins were here before the grass. Before the dirt, even."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.308 set value "Could you fix the roof before it caves in again?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.309 set value "The foundation stones under the church don't match anything we built."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.310 set value "Can we get a proper town center? I keep losing people."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.311 set value "There's a chamber below the well no one dares enter."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.312 set value "Build me a wraparound porch. I want to sit and watch the fields."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.313 set value "The old ones carved warnings into the boundary stones. We just ignore them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.314 set value "Some lantern posts along the road would be helpful after dark."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.315 set value "Ruins don't crumble here like they should. Something holds them together."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.316 set value "I'd love a bakery—smell of bread keeps me sane."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.317 set value "The stonework in the old barrow predates every village on the plains."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.318 set value "Can you dig me a root cellar? My potatoes need a proper home."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.319 set value "Who built the spiral stairs inside the hill? Not us. Not anyone alive."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.320 set value "A little pond with chickens wandering nearby would be perfect."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.321 set value "The engravings on the archway glow when the moon is full."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.322 set value "I want a picnic spot near the tree line. With a proper bench."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.323 set value "Every ruin I've seen has the same three-circle symbol carved deep."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.324 set value "Can you make a stone well that looks like it belongs here?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.325 set value "The old ones didn't just build—they anchored things to the land itself."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.326 set value "Let's get a water trough for the animals. Proper craftsmanship."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.327 set value "Something sleeps beneath the mossy cobblestone. We feel it in the soil."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.328 set value "A small library with cozy corners would be amazing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.329 set value "The carvings tell a story of a sky that broke open. Then healed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.330 set value "Build me a stable. Our horses deserve better than a fence post."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.331 set value "Before the villages, before the mobs—someone else walked these plains."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.332 set value "How about a tree-lined path from here to the next village?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.333 set value "The deepest ruins have doors that open inward but never outward."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.334 set value "A bell tower with a real bell in it—that's all I'm asking for."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.335 set value "I found a tile underground with a map of a land I've never seen."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.336 set value "Build a big sign with the village name. Make it feel official."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.337 set value "The old ones left behind more questions than answers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.338 set value "Make a sitting circle for evening chats. Gossip's a tradition."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.339 set value "Some ruins have heartbeats. Faint, but there. I'm not making it up."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.340 set value "Could you decorate the village with banners? Something warm and bright."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.341 set value "The stones they used don't erode. Rain, wind, nothing touches them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.342 set value "Can you build a chicken coop that blends with the village?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.343 set value "Whoever carved the bedrock was trying to warn us. Or invite us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.344 set value "Build a monument to wheat. It's earned one."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.345 set value "The old pillars lean toward each other, like they're still talking."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.346 set value "Make a hilltop lookout. Gotta spot those pillagers early."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.347 set value "Every ruin hides a crate. Every crate holds a piece of what was."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.348 set value "I want a tree with a swing. Just one. That's the whole request."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.plains.349 set value "The land was shaped by hands older than ours. We just farm on top."
